         <script type="text/javascript">
          jq$(function()
	{
		var gadgetHorMenu = jq$('#id_yOhi7Wr'),
			gadgetHorMenuContainer = gadgetHorMenu.find('.menuInner'),
			firstLevelMenu = gadgetHorMenu.find('ul.firstLevel'),
			holderInitialMenu = firstLevelMenu.children(),
			outsideItems = null,
			phantomElement = '&lt;li class="phantom"&gt;&lt;div class="item"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#x2261;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;ul class="secondLevel"&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;',
			placeHolder = gadgetHorMenu.parents('.WaLayoutPlaceHolder'),
			placeHolderId = placeHolder &amp;&amp; placeHolder.attr('data-componentId');

		function resizeMenu()
		{
			var i,
				len,
				fitMenuWidth = 0,
				menuItemPhantomWidth = 80;

			firstLevelMenu.html( holderInitialMenu).removeClass('adapted').css({ width: 'auto' }); // restore initial menu

			//console.log(firstLevelMenu.width(), gadgetHorMenuContainer.width());


			if( firstLevelMenu.width() &gt; gadgetHorMenuContainer.width() ) // if menu oversize
			{
				menuItemPhantomWidth = firstLevelMenu.addClass('adapted').append( phantomElement).children('.phantom').width();

				for( i = 0, len = holderInitialMenu.size(); i &lt;= len; i++ )
				{
					fitMenuWidth += jq$( holderInitialMenu.get(i) ).width();

					if( fitMenuWidth + menuItemPhantomWidth &gt; gadgetHorMenuContainer.width() )
					{
						outsideItems = firstLevelMenu.children(':gt('+(i-1)+'):not(.phantom)').remove();
						firstLevelMenu.find('.phantom &gt; .item &gt; ul').append( outsideItems);
						break;
					}
				}
				gadgetHorMenu.find('.phantom &gt; .item &gt; a').click(function(){ return false; });
			}

			firstLevelMenu.css( 'width', '' ); // restore initial menu width
			firstLevelMenu.children().removeClass('last-child').eq(-1).addClass('last-child'); // add last-child mark
		}

		resizeMenu();

		jq$(window).resize(function()
		{
			resizeMenu();
		});

		function onLayoutColumnResized(sender, args)
		{
			args = args || {};

			if (placeHolderId &amp;&amp; (placeHolderId == args.leftColPlaceHolderId || placeHolderId == args.rightColPlaceHolderId))
			{
				resizeMenu();
			}
		}

		BonaPage.addPageStateHandler(BonaPage.PAGE_PARSED, function() { WA.Gadgets.LayoutColumnResized.addHandler(onLayoutColumnResized); });
		BonaPage.addPageStateHandler(BonaPage.PAGE_PARSED, function() { WA.Gadgets.StickyPlaceHolderResized.addHandler(resizeMenu); });
		BonaPage.addPageStateHandler(BonaPage.PAGE_UNLOADED, function() { WA.Gadgets.LayoutColumnResized.removeHandler(onLayoutColumnResized); });
		BonaPage.addPageStateHandler(BonaPage.PAGE_UNLOADED, function() { WA.Gadgets.StickyPlaceHolderResized.removeHandler(resizeMenu); });



		var supportTouch = !!(('ontouchstart' in window) || (window.DocumentTouch &amp;&amp; document instanceof DocumentTouch) || (navigator.msPointerEnabled &amp;&amp; navigator.msMaxTouchPoints));

		if( supportTouch )
		{
			jq$('#id_yOhi7Wr').find('.menuInner li.dir &gt; .item &gt; a').on( 'click', function(event)
			{
				if( !this.touchCounter )
					this.touchCounter = 0;

				if( this.touchCounter &gt;= 1 )
				{
					this.touchCounter = 0;
					return true;
				}
				this.touchCounter++;
				event.preventDefault();
			});

			jq$('#id_yOhi7Wr').find('.menuInner li.dir &gt; .item &gt; a').on( 'mouseout', function(event)
			{
				if( !this.touchCounter )
					this.touchCounter = 0;
				this.touchCounter = 0;
			});
		}


	});
         </script>
        </div>
       </div>

                                                             <br/>
                                                             Only Members participating for CEU credits will be given a set of real exam questions based on their own study pace.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Through study groups you can enjoy learning with nice , quite place designed for study groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             SMEI Arabia coordinate with Mobily Top Management in Riyadh to facilitate studying the materials in groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>

                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>

                                                               </font>

                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <font color="#000066" size="5">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               Certified Marketing Executive, CME
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </font>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              Online Training ONLY PART I CME
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <em>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              Free for Golden and Platinum Members Only
                                                             </em>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             (10) hours Only
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <img alt="" border="0" height="225" src="/Resources/Pictures/certifeid.jpg" title="" width="225"/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Training Starts on July 5, 2015
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              In this Training you can Join a virtual class and talk with certified Instructor and you can also have discussions and send questions. This course is a facilitation for exam preparation for CME designation.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              The Certified Marketing Executive, CME training is designed for Managers and is subject for global exam conducted by SMEI USA New York. SMEI is global sales and marketing professional association established in 1935 by IBM founder.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              Certified Marketing Executive, CME discuss the following topics:
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              1) Marketing Management
                                                              <br/>
                                                              2) Business Unit Management
                                                              <br/>
                                                              3) Strategy
                                                              <br/>
                                                              4) Marketing Planning.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              In this type of synchronous training, the communication takes place as a two way conversation , with the trainer and students available in the virtual class online. A special global program will be used for Online training and you will be able to Join online any where.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              You can also send questions to SMEI about the training material after the training.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              Online Training covers the first 10 hours , Part I.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              All golden and platinum members who registered as members before June 30, 2015 will get their training sponsored by SMEI Arabia. Members who Join After June 30, 2015 has to pay the membership and additional online training fees of 650 USD/ participant.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              All Participants will get 10 hours continuous educational units ( 1 CEU), which is a requirement for certificate renewal and for setting for the exam.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              To have Hard copy Certificate issued by SMEI for attending this online training delivered to your address an additional cost of 160 USD is applicable. Soft copy is at 100 USD.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              if you are not a
                                                              <a href="/JOINSMEI">
                                                               member join us now
                                                              </a>
                                                              now before June 30, 2015 and get your online training sponsored by SMEI Arabia.
                                                              <br/>

                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              Certified Marketing Executive, CME
                                                             </font>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              SMEI Certified Professional Sales Person, SCPS
                                                             </font>

                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Al Riyadh- Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              We have also updated the status of member participation to include observing member who can attend free. Any gold or platinum member for CSE and CME can attend free. However, the CEU credit for observing member is not given.
                                                             </span>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <br/>

                                                             <div align="center">
                                                              <img alt="" border="0" height="149" src="/Resources/Pictures/riyadh_city.jpg" style="font-size: 0.9em;" title="" width="200"/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Only Members participating for CEU credits will be given a set of real exam questions based on their own study pace.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Through study groups you can enjoy learning with nice , quite place designed for study groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             SMEI Arabia has appointed a team leaders in Riyadh to facilitate studying the materials in groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>

                                                               CSE

                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>

                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              Certified Sales Executive, CSE discuss the following topics:
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              1) Sales management

                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Dammam - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              We have also updated the status of member participation to include observing member who can attend free. Any gold or platinum member for CSE and CME can attend free. However, the CEU credit for observing member is not given.
                                                             </span>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>

                                                             <div align="center">
                                                             </div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Only Members participating for CEU credits will be given a set of real exam questions based on their own study pace.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Through study groups you can enjoy learning with nice , quite place designed for study groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             SMEI Arabia has appointed a team leaders in Riyadh to facilitate studying the materials in groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>

                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Jeddah - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>

                                                           <div class="inner gadgetEventEditableArea">
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <strong>
                                                              SPECIAL EVENT
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <font color="#000066" size="5">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               Certified Sales Executive, CSE
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </font>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              Part II
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              Online Training
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             (10) hours Only
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <img alt="" border="0" height="225" src="/Resources/Pictures/certifeid.jpg" title="" width="225"/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Training Starts on August 16, 2015
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             ( August 16 - August 20, 2015)
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             6:00 - 8:00 PM Daily
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              In this Training you can Join a virtual class and talk with certified Instructor and you can also have discussions and send questions. This course is a facilitation for exam preparation for CSE designation.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              The Certified Sales Executive, CSE training is designed for Managers and is subject for global exam conducted by SMEI USA New York. SMEI is global sales and marketing professional association established in 1935 by IBM founder.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              Certified Sales Executive, CSE PART II discuss the following topics:
                                                             </div>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <p align="center">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               <span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;">
                                                                Module Two  Part II
                                                               </span>
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <p align="justify">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               <span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;">
                                                                <br/>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <p align="justify">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               <span style="line-height: 115%;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Managing Planing &amp; Evaluation
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <p align="justify">
                                                              <strong>
                                                               <span style="line-height: 115%;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 <br/>
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </strong>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <p align="justify">
                                                              <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                               <font size="2">
                                                                Sales Planning
                                                               </font>
                                                              </span>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="square">
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Forecasting Sales and Developing Budgets
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Sales Territories
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Sales Analysis tools
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>
                                                             <p align="justify">
                                                              <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                               <font size="2">
                                                                Evaluating Sales Performance
                                                               </font>
                                                              </span>
                                                             </p>
                                                             <ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="square">
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Analysis of Sales Volume
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Marketing Cost and Profitability Analysis
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Evaluating a Salesperson's Performance
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li align="justify">
                                                               <span style="line-height: 16px;">
                                                                <font size="2">
                                                                 Ethical and Legal Responsibilities of Sales Managers
                                                                </font>
                                                               </span>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <div align="left">
                                                              In this type of synchronous training, the communication takes place as a two way conversation , with the trainer and students available in the virtual class online. A special global program will be used for Online training and you will be able to Join online any where.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              You can also send questions to SMEI about the training material after the training.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              All Participants will get 1.0 continuous educational units ( CEU, which is a requirement for certificate renewal and for setting for the exam.
                                                              <br/>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              To have Hard copy Certificate issued by SMEI for attending this online training delivered to your address an additional cost of 160 USD is applicable. Soft copy is at 100 USD.
                                                             </div>

Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>

Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>

                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Jeddah - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                             </span>

                                                             <br/>

                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>

                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Al Riyadh- Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>

                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Dammam - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.

                                                              <br/>

                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>

                                                              CSE-CME -SCPS Study Group meeting

                                                            </div>

                                                             <div align="center">
                                                              <font style="font-size: 14px;">
                                                               Enhanced with New CME Book questions

                                                             <b>
                                                              <span style="">
                                                               October 17, 20
                                                               <font face="tahoma, verdana, sans-serif, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_0">
                                                                15

                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              Certified Sales Executive, CSE;

                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center" style="text-align: center;">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              Certified Marketing Executive, CME

                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              SMEI Certified Professional Sales Person, SCPS
                                                             </font>

                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Jeddah - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span style="">
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span style="">
                                                              We have also updated the status of member participation to include observing member who can attend free. Any gold or platinum member for CSE and CME can attend free. However, the CEU credit for observing member is not given.
                                                             </span>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <img alt="" border="0" height="124" src="/Resources/Pictures/Jeddah_Seafront.jpg" title="" width="200"/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <div align="center">
                                                             </div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Only Members participating for CEU credits will be given a set of real exam questions based on their own study pace.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Through study groups you can enjoy learning with nice , quite place designed for study groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             SMEI Arabia has appointed a team leaders in Riyadh to facilitate studying the materials in groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <b>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </b>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>

                                                              <a href="/StudyGroup_KSA">

                                                            <div align="center">

                                                              SMEI Certified Professional Sales Person, SCPS
                                                             </font>

                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Al Riyadh- Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              We have also updated the status of member participation to include observing member who can attend free. Any gold or platinum member for CSE and CME can attend free. However, the CEU credit for observing member is not given.
                                                             </span>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>

                                                              <img alt="" border="0" height="149" src="/Resources/Pictures/riyadh_city.jpg" style="font-size: 0.9em;" title="" width="200"/>
                                                             </div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Only Members participating for CEU credits will be given a set of real exam questions based on their own study pace.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             Through study groups you can enjoy learning with nice , quite place designed for study groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             SMEI Arabia has appointed a team leaders in Riyadh to facilitate studying the materials in groups.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             by participating in this study group SMEI will follow up your progress.
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <strong>
                                                              <br/>
                                                              How SMEI Arabia study group works?
                                                             </strong>
                                                             <br/>
                                                             <ul>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                When you register you will be sent a group of questions for each type of membership programs.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members need to solve the questions
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                All members should sign on questions sheet.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                Members should discuss why the answer could be A, or B, or or C or D.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                              <li>
                                                               <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_5">
                                                                a group picture is taken and sent to SMEI Arabia by team leader.
                                                               </font>
                                                              </li>
                                                             </ul>

                                                              <b>
                                                               November 14, 20
                                                               <font face="tahoma, verdana, sans-serif, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_0">
                                                                15

                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">

                                                            <div align="center" style="text-align: center;">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              Certified Marketing Executive, CME
                                                             </font>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <font face="Open Sans, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3, WaWebKitSavedSpanIndex_3">
                                                              SMEI Certified Professional Sales Person, SCPS
                                                             </font>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div align="center">
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            This is a great chance to  Network with SMEI members in Dammam - Saudi Arabia. Getting the chance to Build relationship and exchange experience. Then study groups not only provides you with networking opportunity but also the chance to organize your learning and studying forSCPS, CSE &amp; CME program.
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              <br/>
                                                             </span>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <span>
                                                              We have also updated the status of member participation to include observing member who can attend free. Any gold or platinum member for CSE and CME can attend free. However, the CEU credit for observing member is not given.
                                                             </span>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div>
                                                             <br/>
                                                            </div>
